Hello. There are some tools.
/vk_add_token - add token to vk.
/get_spy_list - prints all users you are spy on.
/add_to_online_spy - add user to online spy list.
/add_to_friends_spy - add user to friends spy list.
/add_to_wall_spy - add user to wall spy list.
/remove_from_spy - shows you list of user and ask if you want remove anyone.

